================================================================================
Depencies
================================================================================

* SDL2      (http://libsdl.org)
* SDL2_ttf  (http://libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf)


================================================================================
Building the library
================================================================================

You can build SDLU with configure, CMake or premake. See README-configure,
README-cmake or README-premake for more information on using each build system.

* Windows   :  CMake, premake
* Cygwin    :  CMake, configure
* Linux     :  CMake, premake, configure
* Mac OS X  :  CMake, premake, configure
* Android   :  See README-android
* iOS       :  See README-ios


================================================================================
Linking to SDLU
================================================================================

To compile an application that uses the SDL utility library, you can use
'pkg-config', or sdlu-config:

    $ gcc program.c -o program `pkg-config --libs --cflags sdlu` [flags]
    $ gcc program.c -o program `sdlu-config --libs --cflags` [flags]

If you use Mac OS X and built SDLU.framework with CMake:

    $ gcc program.c -o program -framework SDLU [flags]

